	  <concept id="i1071117"
            ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3"
            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">47.207-7</ph> Liability and insurance.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d2742e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2756e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall specify-</p>
					          <ol id="d2742e23" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2756e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contractor’s liability for injury to persons or damage to property other than the freight being transported;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2756e36" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contractor’s liability for loss of and/or dam- age to the freight being transported; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2756e45" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The amount of insurance the contractor is required to maintain.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2756e56" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            When the contractor’s liability for loss of and/or damage to the freight being transported is not specified, the usual measure of liability as prescribed in section11706 of the Interstate Commerce Act (<xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html"
                        class="- topic/xref ">49 U.S.C.11706</xref>) applies.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2756e68" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1045769.dita#i1045769"
                        base="i1045769"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.247-21</xref>, Contractor Liability for Personal Injury and/or Property Damage.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2756e80" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1045781.dita#i1045781"
                        base="i1045781"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.247-22</xref>, Contractor Liability for Loss of and/or Damage to Freight other than Household Goods, in solicitations and contracts for the transportation of freight other than household goods.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2756e92" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1045790.dita#i1045790"
                        base="i1045790"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.247-23</xref>, Contractor Liability for Loss of and/or Damage to Household Goods, in solicitations and contracts for the transportation of household goods, including the rate per pound appropriate to the situation.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2756e105" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(f)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            When freight is not shipped under rates subject to released or declared value, see <xref href="FAR-i1088051.dita#i1088051"
                        base="i1088051"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">28.313</xref>(a) and the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1051209.dita#i1051209"
                        base="i1051209"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.228-9</xref>, Cargo Insurance.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2756e120" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(g)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            When the contracting officer determines that vehicular liability and/or general public liability insurance required by law are not sufficient for a contract, see <xref href="FAR-i1088051.dita#i1088051"
                        base="i1088051"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">28.313</xref>(b) and the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1051223.dita#i1051223"
                        base="i1051223"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.228-10</xref>, Vehicular and General Public Liability Insurance.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
